# Privacy Policy for SeaBus Countdown

Last updated: November 27, 2025

## Location Data
SeaBus Countdown may request access to your location to automatically detect your nearest terminal. Location data is:
- Only used locally on your device
- Never transmitted to our servers
- Never stored or shared with third parties
- Optional - the app works without location access

## Third-Party Advertising
This app uses Google AdMob to display advertisements. AdMob may collect and use data as described in Google's Privacy Policy: https://policies.google.com/privacy

## Data We Don't Collect
We do not collect, store, or transmit any personal information.

## Contact
For questions about this privacy policy, please contact: rowanlean@icloud.com or create an issue here: https://github.com/RomanTheCube/seabus-countdown/issues
